# HTML-first Pipeline Specification

## Pipeline Order

1. **Phase 2: Design-System Extraction** (`.claude/skills/design-system-sync/scripts/validate_figma_extraction.py`)
2. **Phase 3: Figma MCP Extraction** (Save `figma.node-bundle.json`)
